Jadi awak ada apa-apa maklumat?

29
00:03:37,675 --> 00:03:43,681
Dulu semua orang cakap 
Pak Cik Jun yang bunuh dia.

30
00:03:44,849 --> 00:03:47,060
Tapi saya tak percaya.

31
00:03:49,979 --> 00:03:51,105
Choi Chil-seong.

32
00:03:53,483 --> 00:03:55,860
Selepas dia datang ke Geosan,

33
00:03:55,944 --> 00:03:59,614
