Jadi saya fikir tentu dia 
yang bunuh ayah saya.

35
00:04:07,413 --> 00:04:09,832
Entah macam mana dia tahu,

36
00:04:10,667 --> 00:04:14,337
tapi dia mula datang ke kafe saya 
kira-kira dua bulan lepas.

37
00:04:18,091 --> 00:04:20,260
Dia selalu duduk di tempat sama,

38
00:04:21,469 --> 00:04:23,179
minum kopi, kemudian balik.

39
00:04:25,431 --> 00:04:26,557
Suatu hari…

40
00:04:41,739 --> 00:04:43,157
Jemput minum.

41
00:04:44,367 --> 00:04:45,368
Joo Cheol-yong.

42
00:04:51,791 --> 00:04:53,251
Cheol-yong bertemu ajal

43
00:04:54,460 --> 00:04:55,503
sebab saya.

44
00:05:01,301 --> 00:05:03,219
Dia mati sebab saya.

45
00:05:06,055 --> 00:05:07,724
Dia kenal saya.

46
00:05:12,562 --> 00:05:14,522
Dia datang kerana dia kenal saya.

47
00:05:18,526 --> 00:05:20,486
Tapi apa maksud dia,

48
00:05:21,779 --> 00:05:24,282
"Dia mati sebab saya"?

49
00:05:26,284 --> 00:05:27,744
Saya perlu tahu jawapannya.

50
00:05:29,078 --> 00:05:30,496
Jadi saya ikut dia.

51
00:05:33,458 --> 00:05:34,834
Apa maksud awak?

52
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:38,963
Apa maksud awak, dia mati sebab awak?

53
