Tunggu, encik.

62
00:06:32,642 --> 00:06:35,144
Tunggu. Ambil ini.

63
00:06:35,228 --> 00:06:38,523
Ambil duit 40,000 won ini.

64
00:06:40,817 --> 00:06:41,984
Encik.

65
00:06:42,068 --> 00:06:44,904
Ini duit encik. Ambillah.

66
00:06:50,076 --> 00:06:51,661
Tunggu.

67
00:06:51,744 --> 00:06:54,539
Awak mesti ambil 40,000 won ini.

68
00:06:54,622 --> 00:06:56,374
- Saya rasa bersalah… 
- Tapi…

69
00:06:56,457 --> 00:06:57,834
kalau saya tak pulangkan.

70
00:06:57,917 --> 00:07:00,920
kami bertembung dengan orang mabuk.

71
00:07:03,506 --> 00:07:04,841
Kenapa pandang saya?

72
00:07:05,424 --> 00:07:06,884
Awak maksudkan saya?

73
00:07:07,552 --> 00:07:10,012
Awak berkeras mahu dia ambil 40,000 won…

74
