Apabila saya bangun keesokan paginya, 
seluruh kampung kecoh.

91
00:09:05,378 --> 00:09:08,047
Khabarnya, ada kereta 
ditarik dari takungan air

92
00:09:08,714 --> 00:09:12,009
dan ada mayat di dalamnya.

93
00:09:13,302 --> 00:09:15,555
Ceritanya habis di situ.

94
00:09:16,931 --> 00:09:18,641
Malang betul nasib saya.

95
00:09:20,810 --> 00:09:21,644
Tunggu.

96
00:09:23,187 --> 00:09:25,064
Dia ajak awak berjumpa lagi?

97
00:09:36,367 --> 00:09:38,035
Dia suruh jumpa di sana.

98
00:09:38,119 --> 00:09:41,330
Rumah Inap Mawar di Buknam-dong?

99
00:09:42,248 --> 00:09:45,334
Nampaknya dia menginap di sana 
sebelum dia mati.

100
00:09:45,418 --> 00:09:49,755
Dia kata kalau saya jumpa dia di sana, 
dia akan beritahu saya segalanya

101
00:09:49,839 --> 00:09:51,382
dan beri saya sesuatu.

102
00:09:53,134 --> 00:09:54,385
Rasanya ini barangnya.

103
00:09:55,136 --> 00:09:57,555
Saya jumpa di tengah-tengah bilik kosong.

104
00:10:00,558 --> 00:10:01,892
Tunggu. Biar saya buka.

105
00:10:09,233 --> 00:10:10,192
Hei.

106
00:10:11,485 --> 00:10:12,361
Duitlah.

107
00:10:14,363 --> 00:10:15,906
Dia nak beri saya duit?

108
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:17,700
Berapa jumlahnya?

109
00:10:19,243 --> 00:10:21,704
Tapi itu tak penting, bukan?

110
00:10:22,246 --> 00:10:27,835
Saya cuma nak tahu 
siapa bunuh ayah saya dan kenapa.

111
00:10:28,502 --> 00:10:30,004
Saya nak tahu itu saja.

112
00:10:33,299 --> 00:10:36,844
Apa pun, itu saja yang saya tahu.

113
00:10:37,720 --> 00:10:41,223
Saya percaya awak akan uruskan. 
Saya akan tunggu.

114
00:10:42,099 --> 00:10:43,351
Sebab awak polis.

115
00:10:51,776 --> 00:10:52,652
Hei.

116
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:56,405
Dia tahu segalanya.

117
00:10:58,616 --> 00:11:00,618
Saya hargai bantuan dia,

118
00:11:00,701 --> 00:11:03,204
tapi saya masih tak faham 
apa makna semua ini.

119
00:11:03,913 --> 00:11:05,498
Awak faham tak?

120
00:11:05,581 --> 00:11:06,791
Ya.

121
00:11:07,792 --> 00:11:09,001
Awak juga patut faham.

122
00:11:09,669 --> 00:11:10,503
Apa?

123
00:11:12,046 --> 00:11:13,798
Awak masih tak cam dia?

124
00:11:15,466 --> 00:11:16,759
Tidak. Siapa dia?

125
00:11:25,851 --> 00:11:26,894
Dialah budak itu.

126
00:11:27,853 --> 00:11:29,563
JOO CHEOL-YONG

127
00:11:29,647 --> 00:11:31,482
Anak Pak Cik Cheol-yong.

128
00:11:34,652 --> 00:11:35,694
Joo Mi-ran.

129
00:11:36,654 --> 00:11:37,571
Apa?

130
00:11:41,992 --> 00:11:45,496
Du-sik, betulkah awak kembali 
ke Geosan sebab itu?

131
00:11:47,748 --> 00:11:48,666
Betulkah?

132
00:11:50,668 --> 00:11:55,881
Saya sangka awak tak nak ingat lagi 
cerita lama.

133
00:11:58,843 --> 00:11:59,718
Hei.

134
00:12:00,845 --> 00:12:03,514
Saya kemas rumah beberapa hari lepas

135
00:12:03,597 --> 00:12:06,016
dan saya jumpa diari lama saya.

136
00:12:07,059 --> 00:12:10,813
Saya cuma tulis tentang waktu main.

137
00:12:11,730 --> 00:12:14,233
Saya tahu main saja waktu kecil.

138
00:12:15,985 --> 00:12:17,611
Suatu hari,

139
00:12:18,571 --> 00:12:20,448
saya daki gunung dengan kamu semua

140
00:12:20,531 --> 00:12:23,200
dan kita main di sana sampai senja.

141
00:12:23,284 --> 00:12:24,994
Saya seronok sangat

142
00:12:25,703 --> 00:12:27,872
dan saya tulis ini di bawah sekali.

143
00:12:29,832 --> 00:12:31,125
"Alangkah baiknya

144
00:12:32,209 --> 00:12:36,422
kalau detik ini kekal selamanya."

145
00:12:39,300 --> 00:12:42,511
Mungkin hajat itu yang membawa malang.

146
00:12:42,595 --> 00:12:45,389
Tak lama selepas itu, hidup saya hancur.

147
00:12:49,351 --> 00:12:52,980
Awak betul-betul tak cam Mi-ran 
sepanjang tiga tahun lepas?

148
00:12:56,233 --> 00:12:57,610
Hei, Kim Baek-du.

149
00:12:57,693 --> 00:12:59,945
Ya? Apa?

150
00:13:00,029 --> 00:13:04,033
Betulkah awak tak tahu 
Mi-ran anak Pak Cik Cheol-yong?

151
00:13:04,116 --> 00:13:07,203
Ya. Mi-ran.

152
00:13:07,703 --> 00:13:09,997
Saya betul-betul tak tahu.

153
00:13:10,873 --> 00:13:13,209
Awak tahu rancangan The Masked Singer?

154
00:13:13,834 --> 00:13:17,421
Dalam rancangan itu, 
penonton dan juri tak cam peserta

155
00:13:17,505 --> 00:13:18,672
dengan suara saja.

156
00:13:18,756 --> 00:13:20,883
Tapi lebih memalukan

157
00:13:20,966 --> 00:13:24,094
apabila peserta tanggalkan topeng

158
00:13:24,178 --> 00:13:26,430
dan ada yang masih tak kenal.

159
00:13:26,514 --> 00:13:28,474
Itulah perasaan saya sekarang.

160
00:13:31,185 --> 00:13:35,689
Anak Pak Cik Cheol-yong, Joo Mi-ran…

161
00:13:38,567 --> 00:13:39,443
Du-sik.

162
00:13:40,528 --> 00:13:46,534
Sejujurnya, kalau saya di tempat dia, 
saya akan ambil saja duit ini.

163
00:13:51,247 --> 00:13:54,416
Maksud saya, 
cuba awak fikir secara objektif.

164
00:13:54,500 --> 00:13:57,044
Hakikatnya,

165
00:13:57,127 --> 00:13:59,338
elok juga kalau dia dapat pampasan.

166
00:13:59,421 --> 00:14:01,840
Awak rasa duit boleh jadi pampasan?

167
00:14:01,924 --> 00:14:04,843
KEDAI KOPII RAN 
TUTUP

168
00:14:07,721 --> 00:14:11,767
Duit tak cukup untuk menjadi ganti rugi.

169
00:14:16,939 --> 00:14:18,691
Fikirlah tentang kehilangan dia.

170
00:14:38,168 --> 00:14:40,004
Saya pun tak faham sepenuhnya,

171
00:14:40,921 --> 00:14:44,592
tapi mungkin dia rasa macam 
sebelah kakinya tersekat dalam lumpur.

172
00:14:46,302 --> 00:14:48,971
Dia gigih mencuba, 
tapi tetap tak dapat keluar.

173
00:14:50,139 --> 00:14:53,642
Dan tiada siapa datang membantu dia.

174
00:14:54,226 --> 00:14:59,398
Bayangkan tersekat di tempat yang sama 
seumur hidup.

175
00:15:01,525 --> 00:15:03,611
Duit sebanyak mana pun tak dapat…

176
00:15:03,694 --> 00:15:04,945
Awak juga rasa begitu?

177
00:15:05,821 --> 00:15:06,697
Apa?

178
00:15:06,780 --> 00:15:08,574
Sejak meninggalkan kampung ini,

179
00:15:09,283 --> 00:15:12,620
awak juga rasa tersekat 
dalam lumpur seperti itu?

180
00:15:13,203 --> 00:15:14,079
Saya?

181
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:20,127
Ada pasang surutnya bagi saya.

182
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:23,255
Kadang-kadang,

183
00:15:23,339 --> 00:15:26,926
apa saja berkaitan dengan ssireum 
dan Geosan buat saya marah,

184
00:15:28,093 --> 00:15:29,428
dan kadang-kadang,

185
00:15:32,431 --> 00:15:35,392
mengenang hidup saya di sini 
buat saya tersenyum.

186
00:15:38,604 --> 00:15:41,190
Saya cuba nafikan,

187
00:15:41,690 --> 00:15:46,612
tapi zaman kanak-kanak Oh Du-sik di sini 
adalah waktu paling bahagia dalam hidup.

188
00:15:51,492 --> 00:15:53,911
Sudahlah. Awak takkan faham.

189
00:15:54,995 --> 00:15:59,541
Awak tak pernah kehilangan apa-apa 
dalam hidup, awak takkan faham rasanya.

190
00:15:59,625 --> 00:16:00,459
Apa?

191
00:16:01,001 --> 00:16:03,170
Siapa cakap saya tak pernah kehilangan?

192
00:16:03,253 --> 00:16:04,088
Apa dia?

193
00:16:04,797 --> 00:16:06,215
Awak kehilangan apa?

194
00:16:07,466 --> 00:16:10,594
- Macam-macam… 
- Cakaplah.

195
00:16:10,678 --> 00:16:12,513
Contohnya apa?

196
00:16:15,015 --> 00:16:16,141
Saya…

197
00:16:28,862 --> 00:16:30,322
Saya pun pernah kehilangan.

198
00:16:32,199 --> 00:16:33,617
Sebab dia, saya…

199
00:16:36,996 --> 00:16:37,955
Saya…

200
00:16:51,176 --> 00:16:53,470
Angin yang tolak pagar.

201
00:17:01,937 --> 00:17:03,689
Pergi mandi dan makan malam.

202
00:17:04,314 --> 00:17:05,190
Okey.

203
00:17:18,287 --> 00:17:19,121
Ayah.

204
00:17:20,080 --> 00:17:20,914
Apa?

205
00:17:22,374 --> 00:17:23,292
Dulu,

206
00:17:25,210 --> 00:17:28,922
kita tak patut biarkan 
keluarga Du-sik pergi begitu saja.

207
00:17:31,425 --> 00:17:36,305
Kita patut cuba sedaya upaya 
untuk bantu mereka supaya

208
00:17:38,515 --> 00:17:40,017
mereka tak perlu pindah.

209
00:17:42,644 --> 00:17:43,771
Kalau kita bantu…

210
00:19:01,598 --> 00:19:03,767
Saya tahulah mereka kembar,

211
00:19:03,851 --> 00:19:06,645
tapi macam mana boleh dapat 
nombor 197 dan 198?

212
00:19:06,728 --> 00:19:08,564
Itu taklah teruk sangat.

213
00:19:08,647 --> 00:19:12,901
Sayang, kebelakangan ini, mana ada 
500 ke 600 pelajar di sekolah lagi

214
00:19:12,985 --> 00:19:14,111
macam zaman dulu.

215
00:19:14,194 --> 00:19:16,864
Sekolah dia ada lebih kurang 200 pelajar.

216
00:19:16,947 --> 00:19:20,033
Yakah? Jadi mereka hampir corot.

217
00:19:20,117 --> 00:19:23,287
Aduhai, tentu ibu bapa mereka risau.

218
00:19:23,370 --> 00:19:27,916
Ibu mereka minta tolong 
Uk jadi tutor mereka.

219
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:29,042
Yeong-uk?

220
00:19:29,626 --> 00:19:33,046
Kalau dia ambil ujian yang sama, 
tentu dia dapat nombor 199.

221
00:19:34,298 --> 00:19:37,676
Bukan Yeong-uk, tapi Hyeon-uk.

222
00:19:37,759 --> 00:19:41,096
Ingat tak pengurus baru pasukan ssireum?

223
00:19:41,180 --> 00:19:43,473
- Suami dia, Hyeon-uk. 
- Okey.

224
00:19:43,557 --> 00:19:46,018
Dia menganggur sekarang,

225
00:19:46,101 --> 00:19:49,062
tapi saya dengar dia budak pandai 
di sekolah dulu.

226
00:19:49,605 --> 00:19:52,357
Patutlah dia nampak macam orang terpelajar

227
00:19:52,441 --> 00:19:54,443
setiap kali dia bercakap.

228
00:20:01,617 --> 00:20:06,538
Tapi lelaki bijak itu tak tahu 
isterinya buat apa di belakang dia.

229
00:20:10,626 --> 00:20:11,710
Apa maksud awak?

230
00:20:12,628 --> 00:20:13,629
Apa?

231
